{"tid":177132,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"擺低你身上的大小毛病","createTime":"2017-03-28T15:49:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-28T17:16:06.000Z","uid":100347,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6b8e28a29a6415292c5146068737d777562505b5","tid":177132,"uid":100347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T15:49:30.000Z","msg":"左眼：眼角膜 插傷<br />\n<br />\n左耳：大太聲 耳膜會震 懷疑有事<br />\n<br />\n喉嚨：發育時期哮喘+氣管有事，咳到傷聲帶，超容易有痰。宜家講野都無咩氣，仲會被人背後笑<br />\n<br />\n鼻：鼻敏感-&gt;難瞓-&gt;半夜仲未有睡意<br />\n-&gt;黑眼圈八歲開始有<br />\n<br />\n肝：夜瞓傷肝<br />\n<br />\n肺：哮喘底、氣虛，做劇動運動唔緊要，但做到喘會傷氣管，變痰同氣促兩星期<br />\n<br />\n手：右手 姆指食指 懷疑按壓得多，手指向內收縮。 <br />\n指甲同手指中間有塊膜，正常剪指甲剪太入，去到塊膜就會痛，宜家塊膜露出來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔彈結他轉彈琴"},{"pid":"62665571db2547225ca2386602e431f803cc902a","tid":177132,"uid":10842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T15:57:00.000Z","msg":"樣衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd7895d6d315aae98568a5f379e8e938a12d2ec4","tid":177132,"uid":48633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T16:43:44.000Z","msg":"左耳 鼻 同肝晚情況同你差唔多"},{"pid":"a6794188d40ca16541ade2d936f36ac6b64fb759","tid":177132,"uid":57019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T16:44:57.000Z","msg":"嚴重鼻敏感<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n腰痛"},{"pid":"9500c6d9a07f62010b564922c6ceccaf39264646","tid":177132,"uid":27221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T16:57:36.000Z","msg":"關節好易格辣格辣<br />\n由細返風落雨就會腳痛<br />\n行同企得耐 住巴士屈住腳就易腳痛<br />\n懷疑自己有風濕<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有時頭痛<br />\n<br />\n心跳快"},{"pid":"434ba1b9b0a02fe9d2f2148f01d720cbee93148e","tid":177132,"uid":27486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T16:59:50.000Z","msg":"眼㫸毛到生，成日搞到好夠眼屎又吉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇巴絲知點搞？"},{"pid":"727bb2310539d037963169ad9ce929be308b8e1d","tid":177132,"uid":27486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T17:00:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>眼㫸毛到生，成日搞到好夠眼屎又吉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇巴絲知點搞？</blockquote><br />\n多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b332d137e27b64d7c53f6f2645f61fcdc0df9183","tid":177132,"uid":57675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T17:12:03.000Z","msg":"扁平足"},{"pid":"e091d520f1f681634468aa335ab84acee70fbe9c","tid":177132,"uid":83941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T17:16:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}